OL,3,CZoo celebrates UK's first ever birth
OL,4,Cof Elephant Shrews
OL,6,FA pair of rare Elephant Shrews have
OL,7,Fbeen born in the UK, for the first
OL,8,Ftime ever.
OL,10,FThe rare species - also known as Sengi
OL,11,F- were born on 23 February to parents,
OL,12,FNuru and Malaonly.
OL,14,FThe Sengis weigh 30g at birth which is
OL,15,Froughly the same as a double AA
OL,16,Fbattery.
OL,18,FStaff at the zoo were only able to see
OL,19,Fthe pair after they reviewed CCTV
OL,20,Ffootage and emerged from the nest on
OL,21,FThursday 12 March.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
