OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1773418280
OL,3,CZoo celebrates UK's first ever birth
OL,4,Cof Elephant Shrews
OL,6,FThe zoo say it's a "significant
OL,7,Fvictory" for them and the whole of the
OL,8,Fwider Zoological community - they have
OL,9,Fadded to the small handful of the
OL,10,Fanimal that are here already and aid
OL,11,Feducation and study of this African
OL,12,Fspecies.
OL,14,FThe managing director of Hertfordshire
OL,15,FZoo, Tyler Whitnall, said: "To have
OL,16,Fthe first-ever black and rufous sengi
OL,17,Fbirth in the UK right here at
OL,18,FHertfordshire Zoo is an incredible
OL,19,Ffeeling.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
