PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1773418280
OL,3,CZoo celebrates UK's first ever birth
OL,4,Cof Elephant Shrews
OL,6,FWe knew when we welcomed the pair last
OL,7,FOctober that we were part of something
OL,8,Fspecial, but to see them successfully
OL,9,Fbreed so quickly is a testament to the
OL,10,Fworld-class care provided by our team.
OL,12,F"These pups are growing incredibly
OL,13,Ffast and are already showing the same
OL,14,Fhigh-energy, inquisitive traits as
OL,15,Ftheir parents."
OL,17,FThe newborns are currently being
OL,18,Fclosely monitored and being cared for
OL,19,Fby their parents.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/4
